Installation :

    git clone https://github.com/artmees/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks :
    
    ln -s ~/.vim/dotfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/dotfiles/gitconfig ~/.gitconfig

Add the appropriate .bash on the machine :

    MAC OS X :
        ln -s ~/.vim/dotfiles/bash_profile ~/.bash_profile

    Linux ( ubuntu_home , etc.) :
        ln -s ~/.vim/dotfiles/filename ~/.bashrc 
    
    Vagrant :
        ln -s ~/.vim/dotfiles/vagrant_bashrc ~/.bashrc 

Initalizing Submodules Plugins :

    cd ~/.vim/
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
